1. Is `model: "sonnet"` present in the Agent tool call? If not → STOP, add it.
2. Does the dispatch announcement say "Sonnet 4.6" verbatim? If it says "Sonnet 4.5" or just "Sonnet" → STOP, fix to "Sonnet 4.6".

- ❌ "Sonnet 4.5" in announcement (the empirical drift)
